Sur la piste des manuscrits de Tombouctou

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Jean Crepu, published by TV5Monde in 2014 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/b/bb/Sur-la-piste-des-manuscrits-de-Tombouctou-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
On the trail of Timbuktu manuscripts.

It's 2012. With jihadists occupying northern Mali, the incredible rescue of the Timbuktu Manuscripts makes front pages and becomes a symbol around the world. This film recounts the saga of the Malians who risked their lives to protect this world heritage from threat.
